            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>交易台(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TTD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TTD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TTD-US</a>)截至台北時間15日22:49股價下跌3.99美元，報75.15美元，跌幅5.04%，成交量2,643,714（股），盤中最高價78.29美元、最低價75.15美元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.28%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.25%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.75%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.4%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>交易台(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TTD:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TTD\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TTD-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+40.17%</li> <li>近 1 月：+62.71%</li> <li>近 3 月：-1.27%</li> <li>近 6 月：-37.13%</li> <li>今年以來：-32.66%</li></ul></section></main>",
